These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
Transport: scooter, helicopter, subway, bike
1. Transport:bike is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1
2. Beverage:7up is on the left of Transport:helicopter##1
3. Beverage:water is in an odd position##4
4. Transport:subway is on the left or right of Transport:bike##3
5. Beverage:7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Transport        | scooter | helicopter   | bike | subway    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
Flower: daisy, poppy, orchid, dahlia
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
2. Flower:daisy is on the left of Flower:orchid##1
3. Flower:orchid is in an odd position##4
4. Flower:daisy == Movie-Genre:crime##1
5. Flower:poppy is on the right of Flower:orchid##1
6. Flower:daisy == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Flower   | dahlia    | daisy | orchid | poppy    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Birthday: february, october, july, december
Movie-Genre: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. Birthday:december is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:western##3
2. Birthday:july is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Birthday:october##3
4. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1
5. Movie-Genre:animation is in an odd position##4
6. Birthday:october is on the right of Birthday:july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Birthday          | december | july | october    | february      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

