3. Flower:dahlia is in an odd position##4
4. Flower:zinnia is on the left of Flower:marigold##1
5. Flower:zinnia is on the right of Hobby:cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Flower   | dahlia       | bellflower   | zinnia    | marigold  |

