2. Nationality:australian == Job:nurse##1
3. Nationality:indian is on the right of Job:photographer##1
4. Job:manager is on the far left##1
5. Job:freelancer is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
