2. Cigar:fonseca is in an odd position##4
3. Pet:guinea-pig is on the left or right of Cigar:fonseca##3
4. Cigar:fonseca is on the right of Pet:guinea-pig##1
5. Cigar:swisher is between Cigar:fonseca and Cigar:alhambra##2
6. Pet:fish is in an odd position##4
7. Pet:fish is between Cigar:swisher and Pet:goat##2
8. Cigar:swisher is on the left or right of Cigar:alhambra##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Cigar   | alhambra | swisher      | fonseca | tiparillo |
| Pet   | bird  | guinea-pig | fish    | goat            |

