.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Movie-Genre: sports, documentary, crime, epic
Music-Genre: disco, dubstep, electronic, jazz
1. Movie-Genre:sports == Music-Genre:jazz##1
2. Music-Genre:disco is on the right of Movie-Genre:sports##1
3. Music-Genre:jazz is between Music-Genre:disco and Movie-Genre:crime##2
4. Movie-Genre:sports is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:jazz is on the left or right of Music-Genre:disco##3
6. Movie-Genre:documentary is on the left or right of Music-Genre:dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre      | documentary       | crime   | sports | epic |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | jazz        | disco    |

