2. Flower:iris is on the left or right of Flower:bellflower##3
3. Flower:rose is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:pepper is on the left of Food:strawberry##1
5. Food:strawberry is on the right of Flower:bellflower##1
6. Food:pepper is in an even position##4
7. Food:corn == Flower:aconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Flower   | rose | bellflower    | iris       | aconite |
| Food       | kale  | pepper | strawberry | corn  |

