.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
Beverage: almond-milk, milk, juice, 7up
Transport: helicopter, jet-ski, subway, van
1. Beverage:milk is in an even position##4
2. Beverage:milk is on the left or right of Transport:helicopter##3
3. Transport:jet-ski is between Beverage:almond-milk and Transport:helicopter##2
4. Beverage:milk is on the far left or far right##3
5. Transport:subway is on the right of Beverage:7up##1
6. Transport:subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Beverage         | almond-milk | juice   | 7up | milk |
| Transport   | van          | jet-ski | helicopter         | subway  |

 